results.title: Live Laugh Love wall decal-Vinyl sticker
results.description:
Imagine waking up in the morning and reading this Live Every Moment Wall Decal.  Positive reinforcement in the morning is key to becoming a happier person.  The wall decal says, “Live every moment, Laugh every day, Love beyond words.”  Although it could be put on any wall in your house, placing it in your bedroom reminds us that we may not have been happy yesterday but we WILL be happy today.  Motivation, in words in the form of wall art, is priceless.

Measuring 27" wide and 23" high this decal makes a lovely bold statement. 


I use the highest quality, ultra fine matte vinyl in making my wall decals, this gives the appearance of a hand painted design on your wall. It is guaranteed for 5-7 years indoor use. Easily removable, will not damage your paint work. 
I do not use PVC which leaves you with a white or clear border around the edge spoiling the look of the design. 
Please note that vinyl will NOT stick to textured walls or surfaces. It is best to let freshly painted walls dry for at least two weeks before applying vinyl. Some of the newer paint like voc free paint may cause a problem with vinyl. Do not use if your paint work is peeling or flaking. You can use it on smooth dry flat walls, or any other smooth surface such as glass or tile. 

Postage

I always post within 1 working days of cleared payment, if ordered before 1pm.
Your decal will be sent in a secure tracked postage roll for protection. 
International postage typically takes 5-7 working days, outside of Europe, and 3-4 working days for Europe. 
I post every weekday, there is no Saturday collection where I live so if you order on a Friday afternoon after 1-2 pm your item will be sent on Monday.

Returns

I will always refund or exchange an undamaged returned item, unless it is a personalized decal. If for any reasons you are not happy please contact me, customer service is very important to me.
If you accidentally mess a piece up I am more than happy to pop extra bits in the post.

Colour size and custom orders

If you require a custom order, please get in touch, I am more than happy to help.

Feedback

Please see my feedback from other happy customers.
